Install (via SDK manager using Android Studio)

Android SDK:
5.1, API Level 22


Android NDK:
20.0.5594570

Sync once gradle files, then after NDK errors come in, 
check generated file local.properties and add:
ndk.dir=/Users/<username>/Source/Android/Sdk/ndk/20.0.5594570

or your Windows/Linux route to the NDK installed inside the SDK folder

Change directory to Sdk/ndk/21.1.6352462 then
ln -s aarch64-linux-android-4.9 mips64el-linux-android
ln -s arm-linux-androideabi-4.9 mipsel-linux-android

(mips is unsupported and will compile as aarch64 and standar arm)
